The minister spoke against revising the main provision of the
START-2 treaty, but he did not rule out the possibility of
adopting some protocol amendments to it, the report said.
</P>
<P>
Sergeyev noted, "The treaty's make-over is out of the question.
But I hope the Duma with the assistance of the Defense Ministry
will formulate some protocol amendments to it." 
