infrastructures, marketing as well as advertising activities
should be improved in order to achieve the target, he indicated.
</P>
<P>
He also expressed the commission's readiness to work with
regional administrations, government and private organizations in
charge of administering tourist attractions, travel agencies,
tour operators, hotels, restaurants, air lines, the mass media
and other concerned bodies to promote tourism in Ethiopia.
</P>
<P>
According to the commission, about 110,000 tourists visited
the country last year.
</P>
<P>
This year's tourism day under the theme "tourism -- a leading
activity of the 21st century for job creation and environmental
protection" is to be celebrated in 131 countries. 
