Benjamin Netanyahu said that he was 100 percent sure that the
militants had came from the West Bank and not from overseas.
</P>
<P>
Israeli Defense Minister Yitzhak Mordechai said on the same day
that the attackers had received backing in the PNA territories.
</P>
<P>
