remarks about the suicide bombers.
</P>
<P>
Jerusalem was struck by suicide bombings on July 30 and
September 4, killing 25 people and wounding more than 300 others.
</P>
<P>
Israel sealed off the PNA territories following the blasts and
have arrested more than 200 Palestinians in the West Bank,
suspecting them of involvement with Hamas and Islamic Jihad, two
radical Islamic resistance groups. 
