<HEADLINE> Greek Cypriot, Turkish Cypriot Leaders to Meet on </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, September 22 (Xinhua) -- The leaders of the
Greek Cypriots and the Turkish Cypriots will meet to discuss
security matters Friday, September 26, at the residence of the
chief of the Mission of the United Nations Operation in Cyprus,
according to sources from the spokesman's office.
</P>
<P>
The sources said that the meeting was in line with the
agreement reached on September 15.
</P>
<P>
