<HEADLINE> Turkish President Urges to Boost Defense Industry </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, September 22 (Xinhua) -- Turkish President Suleyman
Demirel said here today that Turkey should double efforts to
build its own defense industry system.
</P>
<P>
Addressing a seminar on Turkey's defense industry development,
Demirel stressed that Turkey must base its defense capacity on
its own defense industry, adding that it is of great significance
for state interests.
</P>
<P>
He said if a country wants to live in peace, it must attach
importance to its defense industry to become fully self-reliant
in this respect.
</P>
<P>
Demirel maintained Turkey should further boost its defense
industry and that the Turkish government will help this cause as
much as possible.
</P>
<P>
