Minister Mesut Yilmaz, the Armed Forces Chief of General Staff
Ismail Hakki Karadayi and some cabinet ministers.
</P>
<P>
Turkey, a regional military power, imports from the West nearly
80 percent of the arms demanded by the armed forces, according to
official statistics. 
