president of the ruling Alliance of Democrats, also discussed with
Chevenement Hungary's integration process into the European Union,
which will begin taking in Central and Eastern European countries
in 1999.
</P>
<P>
Kuncze will visit the headquarters of the Interpol in Lyon on
Tuesday to discuss with Interpol officials cooperation between the
world cops' organization and Hungary. 
