<TEXT>
<P>
TIANJIN, September 23 (Xinhua) -- A voluntary community
association in north China's Tianjin city received 45,000 yuan in
donation from the Canada Fund today, as a means of helping
education in the community.
</P>
<P>
The community association was sponsored in 1989 by citizens
living along the Xinxing Street in the city's Heping District.
</P>
