ensure that the Games are in good hands," said General Chettha
Thanajaro.
</P>
<P>
"I fully understand and am aware of your concerns" over delays
in preparing for the Games, he said in a speech to the OCA
executive board. "Please be assured that the Thai government has
given its fullest support to these Games."
</P>
<P>
Other Thai officials listed the work that has been achieved to
date and tried to reassure the OCA that all the preparations would
be ready on time. 
