<HEADLINE> 85 killed in massacre in Algeria </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ALGIERS, September 23 (Xinhua) - Islamic fundamentalist rebels
killed 85 civilians and wounded 67 overnight Monday in a suburb
of Algiers, security services said Today.
</P>
<P>
But survivors put the death toll to 180-200.
</P>
<P>
Thirty-one of those injured are in serious condition, the security
services said. 
</P>
