<HEADLINE> Chinese Premier Meets Former US President in HK </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, September 23 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Premier Li Peng met
with former U.S. President George Bush here this morning, discuss
Hong Kong, China-US relations and other issues.
</P>
<P>
George Bush is here attending the annual meetings of the World
Bank Groups and International Monetary Fund (IMF), which opened
today.
</P>
<P>
